  • Constructor Details

    • Notification

      public Notification​(com.vaadin.flow.component.UI ui, java.lang.String title, java.lang.String body, java.lang.String icon)
      Create a new Notification. Be sure to use Notify.createNotification(String, String, String) in order to use the same UI.
      Parameters:
      ui - where the notification will be displayed - has to match the UI in Notify's default constructor.
      title - the title of the notification
      body - the body of the notification
      icon - the icon of the notification (uri, filepath or url)
